metadata.name: The Goddess Athena
metadata.description:
Athena, also spelled Athene, in Greek religion, the city protectress, goddess of war, handicraft, and practical reason, identified by the Romans with Minerva.

It may have been taken as a 4 minute exposure but It took me 3 hours to get it as close to what I wanted it to be after so many trials and error.

Long Exposure - Light Painting Artwork
1 shot exposure, No Photoshop, 4minute Exposure. 
Fujifilm X-T4 + FUJIFILM XF 33mm f/1.4
